{
  "id": "RAW_0aa5fa50",
  "title": "DeepMind 新论文炸锅：AI 全自动进化算法，写出专家都想不到的解，网友：这可能就是“王牌”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651276826&idx=2&sn=8c332905db7bd08e40f45099a37bb3ea",
  "date": "2026-03-02 07:11:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | 木子 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">说起 AI Coding，之前很多人好歹还有个“心理安慰”：AI 也就写写“脚手架代码”、补补前端页面，真到核心算法、业务逻辑，还是得人来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这道“最后防线”，也正在松动。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌 DeepMind</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;最近做了一件更狠的事：他们让&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM 驱动的智能体，直接去改写、进化算法代码本身</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">——不是调参数，而是改算法逻辑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">改完就丢进真实博弈环境里反复跑，自动评测、优胜劣汰，一轮轮进化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果呢？它真的做出了</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">全新的多智能体学习算法</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，在多项测试中超过了人类专家手工打磨的版本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">重要的是，这些机制并不直观，属于人类很难靠经验穷举出来的解。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">更关键的是：人只用定义好了算法骨架，之后的搜索、修改、筛选，全程自动完成，不用手调参数，不用反复试错，也不靠研究者的直觉微调。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.092979127134725\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1054\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173367\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78587c02&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5XBUEsicvdWUexZcmkTNCMrHlJxZMwbiaHWt0uCaxdwEUtDbia9piakq8SZrgTaZj6ibyUGGiapIGpjziaibaAY6p9sAL8mZolBxRU6hk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个智能体叫&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，延续了 DeepMind 一贯的“Alpha”命名传统（AlphaGo、AlphaZero、AlphaFold）。其中 “Evolve” 意为“进化”，点明它的核心机制：通过类似生物进化的方式不断改写和筛选算法。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个 AlphaEvolve 本身去年就有，但这是它&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一次被用来学习算法</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它把 Gemini 系列大模型，和进化搜索结合起来，把代码不断生成、测试、筛选、再进化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3247232472324723\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2710\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173368\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a70b82ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5byDSL2f5ESg4bQ5jcteFAzkehyXpGLZg2ugDwlkkWpJYvFzdKZbP6z5hSWA2yxdMiaFCl6uGubEwTOfFTCJRuRgakgNGrpqmI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepMind 把把研究过程和成果写成了一篇 37 页的论文，题为《基于大语言模型的多智能体学习算法自动发现》（Discovering Multiagent Learning Algorithms with Large Language Models</span><span leaf=\"\">），一发出来就炸了技术圈。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8434782608695652\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1380\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173366\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e915fdf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm7oEE5dZAahyKPKNI2Cyd0Csk0RicBicPG5HLHVCSicsDbCKeKkQEtt0icQZp24vbZ9KPfQD3kQy6sFfF7FqXjdR6T7uk04aE3ib5Sg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有网友看完直呼，这玩意真挺“可怕”的：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“这看起来像是 DeepMind 手中的一张王牌，我认为它可能导致谷歌赢得比赛。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9089219330855018\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1076\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173365\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f56987c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6vibO3omjm7icGm4WaH3GQ11fibrJ4If7ZTwHrJ0uZz29MJsNHHDJV4xPwmEVdHStQjGCBonNIMQvhnGmIoDN4uI0rT3xmm2MMRU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人锐评：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">“这就像教一个孩子读书，然后看着它自己编写教科书。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22727272727272727\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1056\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173364\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bba60cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4OQx93IPhsAPxULfNFvSibTTldAsrQX1mssFmuicoy2ibqiaNpxUSRbdeTF7Ica2wxicUuhEeZlKic5gXBv9pZow1xMicjEPe92ibSvs0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有人已经开始往更远处想：既然 AI 已经能设计更好的学习算法，那或许它也该先给自己设计一套更完善的“伦理引擎”，在 ASI 真正爆发之前，先把对齐这件事想清楚。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39571150097465885\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1026\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173370\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6144eb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm50H3depn5urrR1xrd83SKs0N3yKQW11NjBqaFzruKfIKeyd0gfX1L0yiaqlLGIT5OyEscvUnFNjVU7tVMhibTXnpia3ic4FNQK3xg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1af1aa69&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaICwJicjIwBNeictWsFER7h65DFz5U4uh7icx1jPTSXcJibxtSI2cePlSib0S2ve0cw3X3sozXsCiaVuldXkXkCicnJOWzHX5z1k4Brk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;人只选定算法框架，</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span leaf=\"\">AI 全自动闭环进化</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">来展开看看实验设计和操作过程。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">需要说明的是，研究团队没有让模型“从零写算法”，而是选定两个&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">成熟框架：</span></strong></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">CFR（后悔最小化）：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">CFR 算法族，依赖递归定义来累积后悔值并构建平均策略。</span></span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">PSRO（策略种群训练）：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">通过迭代计算最优响应并求解元策略，不断扩展策略种群。</span></span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去，在不完全信息博弈求解（比如扑克）中，像 CFR、PSRO 这些经典算法虽然理论扎实，但真正好用的“升级版”，还是要靠人类专家一点点凭经验调参、改规则、试出来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后，研究人员把算法核心逻辑，拆成几个可被改写的 Python 函数，例如：regret 累积规则、当前策略生成方式、平均策略更新规则、PSRO 的 meta-solver 逻辑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">也就是说，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们只开放了“关键决策逻辑”给 LLM 改，其余框架固定。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这一步很关键，相当于给进化定义“基因范围”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来就进入真正的“进化环节”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve 把当前算法代码当作“个体”，由 LLM 生成若干语义上有意义的改写版本：不是随便乱改，而是改具体逻辑、控制流或更新规则。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一个改写后的版本，都会被自动编译、运行，然后丢进一组博弈环境里真实对战，用 exploitability 这样的指标打分。表现更好的版本被保留下来，作为下一轮搜索的基础；表现差的直接淘汰。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程是闭环的：生成 → 运行 → 评估 → 筛选 → 再生成，循环推进。人类不参与中间调参，也不手动筛选，只负责设定规则和评价标准。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6460055096418733\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1452\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173373\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a05de117&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5KqpyuLcawvyAcY7XDSmtAD7v2OfTCiaeDUWQzjKTibnFUnsKicP9XwibtYG95Zkmo6m1oicnbFNica9zIciaTkejQUpiajXm6QnkIATM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图注：这张示意图也是 AI 做的</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果，AI 进化出了</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">两个全新算法</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">先看 CFR 这一派。AlphaEvolve 进化出了 VAD-CFR。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 没有去调那点小参数，而是直接改了“后悔值怎么累计、怎么打折、什么时候开始平均策略”这些核心逻辑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如引入了 volatility-sensitive discounting（根据波动动态折扣）、hard warm-start schedule（前期蓄力、后期发力）这样的机制。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">听起来挺抽象的，但效果明显：在多个博弈里，它超过了目前人类手工打磨出来的最强版本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6811397557666214\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1474\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173371\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d12c5040&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5MQzrwKKWxgzDHHmH3kVqJIo3d7kg8HcDCZDffIbkPjyrZGOyIGxyPceDslTzKppH5lSY25yPYpLbEEAgSjicmce9DiatF2SGx4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这张图很直观，展示了多种 CFR 变体在不同博弈环境中的收敛表现。上半部分是用于搜索阶段的训练游戏，下半部分是规模更大、更复杂的测试游戏。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">横轴是迭代次数（最多 1000 次），纵轴是 exploitability（越低越接近均衡）。曲线降得越快、越低，说明算法越强。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">灰色那条线就是 VAD-CFR。可以看到，在多数游戏里，它下滑得更快、落得更低，明显压过 CFR+、DCFR、PCFR+ 这些人类优化过多轮的版本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在一些游戏中，大约 500 次迭代之后，曲线像突然“踩了油门”，下降速度明显加快——这正是它预热阶段结束、正式发力的时刻。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">前半段像是在默默蓄力，后半段才真正冲刺。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">更关键的是，在规模更大、难度更高的测试游戏中，VAD-CFR 依然比传统的 CFR、CFR+、DCFR 等人工设计的算法收敛更快、结果更优，没有出现“只会做模拟题”的情况。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这说明，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不是针对训练游戏做了小技巧，而是在算法结构层面找到了一种更高效的更新方式。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">再看&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">PSRO</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这一派：AI 进化出了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">SHOR-PSRO</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;算法。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它做的事情很简单也很大胆：重新设计“元求解器”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统方法要么偏探索，要么偏逼近均衡，权衡是固定的。而 SHOR 直接把多种更新机制混合在一起，设计了一种混合型 meta-solver，而且随着训练进程动态调整，让训练过程自动从“多样性探索”过渡到“逼近均衡”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6925207756232687\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1444\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100173372\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ce78be1b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4GY0OlKgZsRyUonT0VRiayQDdWpURn6xvrxfdPRibIrM1NenwTNFYWhhQQS6ooaVWAWX9ZDKQWJrQwVsUicU0D1uMdZ3W5wNQ3ok%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这张图，展示的就是它和 Uniform、Nash、AlphaRank、PRD、RM 等经典方法的对比。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">图中不同颜色代表不同元求解器：Uniform、Nash、AlphaRank、PRD、Regret Matching（RM），以及进化得到的 SHOR（棕色线）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">整张图分为上下两部分。上半部分是训练游戏，下半部分是规模更大、更复杂的测试游戏，用来检验算法是否具有泛化能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">横轴是 PSRO 迭代次数（最多 100 轮），纵轴是 exploitability（可被利用度，对数坐标）；数值越低，说明算法越接近博弈均衡、表现越好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，在多数游戏中，SHOR 曲线下降更快，而且在第 100 次迭代时的 exploitability 更低，说明它在同样迭代次数下更有效地逼近均衡。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其是在更复杂的测试游戏中（如 4-player Kuhn、6-sided Liar’s Dice），SHOR 依然保持优势，没有明显退化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单说，SHOR-PSRO 在“什么时候多探索、什么时候专注逼近均衡”这件事上，比传统方法更灵活、更聪明。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不是靠调参数赢的，而是把调度逻辑本身改了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">论文地址：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.16928\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.16928</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://x.com/hasantoxr/status/2026371848217456738\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/hasantoxr/status/2026371848217456738</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/?utm_source=chatgpt.com</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepMind 推出 AlphaEvolve 框架，利用大模型自动进化多智能体学习算法，在复杂博弈任务中超越了人类专家设计的经典算法。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepMind 推出 AlphaEvolve 框架，利用大模型自动进化多智能体学习算法，在复杂博弈任务中超越了人类专家设计的经典算法。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了谷歌 DeepMind 的最新研究成果 AlphaEvolve。该系统利用 Gemini 大模型驱动的智能体，通过模拟生物进化的方式自动改写和优化算法代码。研究团队将 CFR（后悔最小化）和 PSRO（策略种群训练）等经典博弈算法框架的核心逻辑开放给 LLM 进行迭代修改，并在真实博弈环境中进行自动评测与筛选。实验结果表明，AlphaEvolve 进化出的 VAD-CFR 和 SHOR-PSRO 算法在收敛速度和可利用度（exploitability）上均优于人类手工打磨的版本。这一突破标志着 AI Coding 正在从编写基础脚手架代码向自动发现核心算法逻辑演进。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AlphaEvolve 实现了从“辅助写代码”到“自动进化算法”的跨越。",
      "explanation": "系统不再仅仅补全代码，而是通过 LLM 修改算法的核心逻辑函数，如后悔值累积规则和元求解器逻辑，实现了算法层面的创新。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用“生成-运行-评估-筛选”的闭环进化机制。",
      "explanation": "人类仅需定义算法骨架和评价标准，AI 负责在定义的“基因范围”内进行大规模搜索和迭代，全程无需人工干预调参。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 进化的算法在复杂博弈环境中展现出更强的泛化能力。",
      "explanation": "新算法 VAD-CFR 和 SHOR-PSRO 在未见过的复杂测试游戏中依然保持高性能，证明其在结构层面找到了比人类经验更高效的更新方式。"
    }
  ],
